      propertyPath: dialog.welcomeText
      value: Hello Stranger, What brings you here?
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 1083630612538445653, guid: 4e7bfaf0ddf9cf345bf336a305880da7, type: 3}
      propertyPath: dialog.dialogQueries.Array.size
      value: 2
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 1083630612538445653, guid: 4e7bfaf0ddf9cf345bf336a305880da7, type: 3}
      propertyPath: dialog.dialogQueries.Array.data[0].text
      value: I'm a Warden. I'm here to help you return this place to order. Do you
        have something for me?
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 1083630612538445653, guid: 4e7bfaf0ddf9cf345bf336a305880da7, type: 3}
      propertyPath: dialog.dialogQueries.Array.data[1].text
      value: Goodbye
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 1083630612538445653, guid: 4e7bfaf0ddf9cf345bf336a305880da7, type: 3}
      propertyPath: dialog.dialogQueries.Array.data[2].text
      value: Not your buissnes
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 1083630612538445653, guid: 4e7bfaf0ddf9cf345bf336a305880da7, type: 3}
      propertyPath: dialog.dialogQueries.Array.data[0].answer.text
      value: You have no idea how glad I am to hear this. We are in troubles for
        months and besides that, now there is somethig weird in southwest forest.
        Nobody else saw it.  In night I can see ligths between south end of forest.
        My grandma told me stories about haunted place there. And now nobody belives
        me! I promised, I saw it few times. Please, because we have to many troubles
        now, nobody will dare to go there and check it,could you do it?
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 1083630612538445653, guid: 4e7bfaf0ddf9cf345bf336a305880da7, type: 3}
      propertyPath: dialog.dialogQueries.Array.data[1].answer.text
      value: See you
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 1083630612538445653, guid: 4e7bfaf0ddf9cf345bf336a305880da7, type: 3}
      propertyPath: dialog.dialogQueries.Array.data[2].answer.text
      value: Get lost
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 1083630612538445653, guid: 4e7bfaf0ddf9cf345bf336a305880da7, type: 3}
